  "description": [
    "ft tF 1 WATCH THIS PAPER GROW ITS THE PEOPLES PAPER INVEST IN THRIFT STAMPS VOL I Hew to ihe Line Let the Chips Fly Where They May TRUTH AND FAIR DEALING IS ALWAYS BEST POLICY Plain Statement Regarding Views and Policy of the Leader on Questions Pertaining to General Welfare Some time since under the caption of Oh Consistency Thou Art a Jewel we ran a little article refer ing to the apparent inconsistency of a certain merchant whose words and actions were so diametrically at varience that we considered the mat ter worthy of attention The article has called forth many words of ap preciation and praise from our readers generally and received com pliments from sources least expected Jt has also occasioned some adverse criticism from a few who questioned the motive prompting its publication and who accused us of attempting to Create discord and dissention between Organized labor and the business in terests of the city and to disrupt the pleasant relations now existing between labor and capital Nothing could be further from our intentions or more at varience with the policy of this paper We believe that labor and capital should work together each striving"
